{"tid":1459304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地唔應該將個道德標准放到咁高","createTime":"2019-08-12T16:51:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T05:11:36.000Z","uid":21937,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ee5a4f4463545775ee3fe56e00f018cae1b1a18f","tid":1459304,"uid":21937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:51:09.000Z","msg":"日本社運就係將個標准放得太高<br />\n所有做得唔夠個standard 既人都都比人認為唔忠於個運動 最後搞到日本社運死曬<br />\n我地唔洗將個道德標准放到太高<br />\n唔通依家我地又blame 所有有番工既人<br />\n所有同朋友食飯既人<br />\n所有有娛樂既人<br />\n我知道依家香港人只需要槍口對外<br />\n對住個垃圾政權同佢既武裝<br />\n與其set 到個道德標准咁高 單純用朋輩壓力比人<br />\n不如真係真心令到佢地明白到依家既迫切性<br />\n令到佢地有種感覺對政權係真心既憤怒<br />\n唔係靠逼 係靠感染人地 將社會氣氛渲染垃圾政權既恐怖性 唔係令人感到會比人排斥而去關注下件事<br />\n如果唔係每人都有呢種心態 個運動好快會比某d 人搶曬道德高地<br />\n將d 佢地認為唔夠&quot;忠心&quot;既人 排斥<br />\n最受又比人分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c94ad7d24260fb50ab6ff890f38f10529283b1e3","tid":1459304,"uid":21937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:52:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"820426b7df820293623353dcc39cbba7f918f066","tid":1459304,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:53:05.000Z","msg":"721 811 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97398d2464123fa20ca06bb9bc63c50b486c89f9","tid":1459304,"uid":21937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:58:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"08b90ef0bfdf2893d66212e44a6403babdb079bf","tid":1459304,"uid":49756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:03:02.000Z","msg":"「獨立思考」給有意塞鐵嘅手足一段話<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1459323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1459323</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8ae993fee3cef744a43e5e3901f1b9f1450b6746","tid":1459304,"uid":21937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:05:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95a295904f75849e45a80342394919cd12991476","tid":1459304,"uid":1102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:06:34.000Z","msg":"721811"},{"pid":"718836301b17d3a1e75fa2b00780c00c99bbdae1","tid":1459304,"uid":21937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:12:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a816b6541abab0542a87cd4fe2625901a8ab814","tid":1459304,"uid":96869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:15:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc532277a48eb4f7f9b09e3e018a7545a07ce5da","tid":1459304,"uid":3841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:18:25.000Z","msg":"革命融入生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攰就抖下！<br />\n抖完先有力繼續戰鬥！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光<span style=\"color: gold;\">復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"187127593ae2192a41bc2c2fdcf36706b585242b","tid":1459304,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:19:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9bbada7a078dc756b55ab75ed76969d202b1c6a0","tid":1459304,"uid":21937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:43:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c2d263d715dabdeddb371640ff9379d126bec40","tid":1459304,"uid":21937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:02:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f748ad8ab549f6c454c0a1325050043e591d731","tid":1459304,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:08:11.000Z","msg":"<em><strong>一頂綠帽，一條條例，一件柒婆，一個城市，一群市民，<br />\n引發全球二次大蕭條，導致世界第三戰，絕滅支共誰會知?</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />絕不忘記721、811 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nIf we burn, you burn with us</span>"},{"pid":"1c74cd5c70723c28002a461f